rComments: She is a very kind person, but an absolutely horrible teacher. Lectures are poorly prepared,presented, and often ran over class time. Rubrics and other material was often promised but never given, little to no information was given about exams or the content it will contain. If taught by a qualified professor, the course would've been much better.

This course was a lot more interesting when it was taught by someone else. There is a lot of homework, and it is hard to get a good grade in her class unless she likes you. Her comments and feedbacks is not helpful at all, which is making this class even worse. The other classes that she teaches is pretty bad too.
